snippet.title: DEAD OR ALIVE 6 x KOF IV - Mai and Kula Trailer
snippet.description:
5th DLC "THE KING OF FIGHTERS XIV Mashup"New Characters "Mai Shiranui" and "Kula Diamond" will join DOA6!!Don't miss their Beautiful Break Blows!! #KOFXIV #DOA6

DEAD OR ALIVE 6 is available now for purchase on PlayStation4, Xbox One and Steam for PC
